LME Says Grillo of Wilhelm Grillo to Join Boards Next Month

-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 
2011-04-14T17:01:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/lme-says-grillo-of-wilhelm-grillo-to-join-boards-next-month-1-.html
The London Metal Exchange said
Gabriela Grillo of  Wilhelm Grillo Handelsgesellschaft mbH  will
join the boards of LME Holdings Ltd. and The London Metal
Exchange Ltd. next month.  Grillo will join as trade director and succeed Gerd
Hoffmann, who is retiring, the LME said in a notice to members
today. The appointments take effect at the end of the companiesâ€™
annual general meetings, scheduled for May 20, it said.  Gavin Prentice of broker Marex Financial Ltd. was re-
elected as shareholder representative director to the board of
LME Holdings Ltd., the exchange said. Fabian Somerville-Cotton
of HSBC Bank plc was re-elected as shareholder representative
director to the boards of LME Holdings Ltd. and The London Metal
Exchange Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
